febb5ced3270"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Here, we force the numerical evaluation in the definition of the tensor to \
transform the entries into float types for posterior comparisons.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9918082588907337`*^9, 3.9918082635329647`*^9}, {
   3.99180853562397*^9, 3.991808537637763*^9}, 3.991808570991187*^9, {
