Cell["\<\
Finally, applying the quantum circuit operator to the initial state, \
multiplied by the normalization constant, we manage to get the original \
probability vector p:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.991811724310844*^9, 
  3.99181176064581*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a1a068a-765d-4f7e-9d83-\
